In-Game Account Switcher Privacy Statement

1. No your data will be sent to authors of this modification.

2. Some of your data (access_token, refresh_token) will be stored on your device in order to save your Microsoft accounts.

3. Some of your data will be sent to Mojang Studios, Xbox Game Studios, and Microsoft Corporation in order to process an authorization request.

4. This privacy statement may be updated in the future.
